name: Committed Budget Report
query:
SELECT distinct
	com.account as "Account:Link/Account:250", 
	com.cost_center as "Cost Center:Link/Cost Center:250", 
	com.po_no as "Purchase Order:Link/Purchase Order:200", 
	com.po_date as "Commit Date:Date:100",
	com.amount as "Amount:Currency:150"
FROM `tabCommitted Budget` com 
WHERE docstatus = 1 and not exists (select 1 from `tabConsumed Budget` cb where cb.account = com.account and cb.cost_center = com.cost_center and cb.com_ref = com.po_no and cb.item_code = com.item_code);
